abstract: NBA Roundup; Los Angeles Clippers defeat Chicago Bulls, 120-93; other basketball scores noted.
lead_paragraph: The Clippers’ Jamal Crawford led the way with 26 points in a 120-93 victory over the Chicago Bulls in Los Angeles on Sunday.

headline.main: Solid Bench Effort Propels Clippers to Victory Over Bulls
